{"tid":2070216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被波頓書中指與川普有嫌隙 Pompeo批評波頓是「破壞美國的叛徒」","createTime":"2020-06-19T03:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T04:28:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54b97a3f1e9b30c4662c5e529b6190ce5db756d8","tid":2070216,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:36:45.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國前國家安全顧問波頓（John Bolton）即將出版的新書在美國政界引起軒然大波，書中對美國總統川普多有批評，並提及川普與國務卿龐皮歐之間的嫌隙，對於該書，龐皮歐發表聲明痛批波頓「破壞美國的叛徒」。<br />\n<br />\n《商業內幕》報導，美國國務卿龐皮歐稱波頓為破壞美國的叛徒，在他的聲明中表示，他尚未閱讀波頓的書，但書中充滿著謊言，波頓的書名為《事發之室：白宮回憶錄》（The Room Where It Happened: A White House Memoir），龐皮歐則發表了「我也在那房間」聲明（I Was In The Room Too），痛批波頓是背叛人民神聖信任，破壞美國的叛徒，並強調總統川普帶領的美國是造福世界的力量。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3202611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3202611&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C7Hzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=617b1429\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3202611&h=03b3cad5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3202611</a>"},{"pid":"a3eab563bd4649033f789a5cbc114b1cd5af8a8b","tid":2070216,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"美國都咁多分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3398ac0e982b4d229263d4926c5f76688dd591bd","tid":2070216,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3eab563bd4649033f789a5cbc114b1cd5af8a8b","tid":2070216,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"美國都咁多分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/